item.title: Learning Over Earning
item.description: An apprenticeship is a season in your career when your focus is more on your own growth than almost anything else. This is a time for you to delay your ambitions of immediately maximizing your earning potential in order to maximize your learning opportunities. – Apprenticeship Patterns by O’Reilly Media
